abilities.name: Idle
abilities.description: Requires +1 additional unit to upgrade

pieces.name: Cargo Technician
pieces.notes: Base off the lizard from the comics.

abilities.name: Order supplies
abilities.description: Increase attack speed and range of this piece and a friendly ally.

abilities.name: Toxic Syringes
abilities.description: Subsequent attacks on the same target deal increased damage.

abilities.name: Forensics
abilities.description: Mark a target. That unit takes 100% increased damage.

abilities.name: Mop floor
abilities.description: Mops an area around the janitor. ANY other unit that moves in that area is stunned for a few seconds.

abilities.name: Surgery
abilities.description: Heal/damage 1/2/3 nearby allies/enemies respectively.

abilities.name: Invisible Walls
abilities.description: This unit gains massive armor for a short duration.

abilities.name: Beepsky Barrage
abilities.description: Channel an attack on a single enemy, repeatedly stunning and dealing damage to them.

abilities.name: Buy Proto-kinetic Accelerator
abilities.description: Temporarily become melee, gaining increased damage, and splash damage on attacks.

abilities.name: Pie Cannon
abilities.description: Deal massive damage and a lengthy stun to a single target.

abilities.name: Close Quarter Cooking
abilities.description: Despite being ranged, the Cook will melee nearby enemies for increased damage.

abilities.name: Self-repair
abilities.description: Rapidly regenerate health over the course of a few seconds.

abilities.name: Hulk
abilities.description: This piece and all surrounding ones gain increased damage, but become silenced.

abilities.name: Xenobiology
abilities.description: Summon a random slime

abilities.name: Flash grenade
abilities.description: Throw a grenade that damages and silences enemies in an area for 4/8/12 seconds

abilities.name: Upgrade
abilities.description: Give all nearby friendly pieces energy and reduce their cooldowns.

abilities.name: Plasma Flood
abilities.description: Set fire to an area, dealing 3/5/7 % max health damage to all enemies inside of it every second.

abilities.name: Buckshot Pellets
abilities.description: Damage and stun nearby enemies.

abilities.name: Defibrillator Unit
abilities.description: Stun an enemy unit. Enemy units adjacent to that are also stunned. This repeats until the there are no more units to stun.

abilities.name: Call M.U.L.E.B.O.T.
abilities.description: After a few seconds, an area will be hit with a MULEBOT, damaging and stunning enemies.

abilities.name: Exosuit Fabricate
abilities.description: Enter an exosuit, gaining bonus stats and summoning 1/2/3 mechs.

abilities.name: Virus
abilities.description: Starts a virus, which spreads to nearby pieces every second. Heals/damages allies/enemies respectively. Viruses stack.

abilities.name: Brig
abilities.description: Stasis an enemy

abilities.name: Grow tree
abilities.description: Begin growing a tree. Once grown, It will fall, dealing massive damage in a line to enemies.

abilities.name: Build Your Own Shuttle
abilities.description: Begin building a shuttle until this unit is killed or silenced. The shuttle will then crash on enemies, dealing damage proportional to the time it was spent being built.

abilities.name: Brainwashing Surgery
abilities.description: After a lengthy channel, convert an enemy unit.

abilities.name: Promote
abilities.description: Raise the rank of an ally by 1 ‚≠ê

abilities.name: Open Armory
abilities.description: Give all adjacent units increased damage and attack speed.

abilities.name: Override Protocol
abilities.description: At the start of combat, convert all enemy silicons.

abilities.name: Bike Siren
abilities.description: Stun all enemy pieces.

abilities.name: Activate E.X.P.E.R.I.M.E.N.T.O.R.
abilities.description: Change the allegiance of the weakest allied piece in exchange for the strongest enemy piece
